  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Season the cod fillets with salt and black pepper.",
    "Heat the olive oil in a pan over medium heat and sear the cod fillets until cooked through.",
    "Wrap each cod fillet in a pandan leaf and place on a baking sheet.",
    "Drizzle the caramelized sugar sauce over the cod fillets.",
    "Top each cod fillet with pickle slices and a squeeze of lemon juice.",
    "Bake in the oven for 5 minutes to warm the pandan leaves.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy.",
    "Garnish with additional pickle slices and lemon wedges if desired."
